PrecisOrder fixing TUESDAY, MAY 1, 2001, as the day upon which the references to the Hamilton Port Authority in sections 162, 184 and 194 of the Canada Marine Act, being chapter 10 of the Statutes of Canada, 1998 [BILL C-9], shall COME INTO FORCE, as well as sections 198, 199 and 200 thereof, together with Item 3 of Part 1 of the schedule thereto.
